# VHS tape: `rly welcome` first-run onboarding
# Render with: vhs demo/welcome.tape
# Output: demo/welcome.gif
#
# Note: `rly welcome --reset` is interactive — each step waits for Enter.

Output demo/welcome.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "rly welcome --reset"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 3s
